    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Grudge of the Devoured Burns Hotter Than Hell!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pudding Guy once dreamed of sweet love. But the moment he was eaten by humans, his dream was shattered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now awakened at the bottom of hell, only one thing remains: merciless revenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288560/extras/5de6350f5fb0c8e9787e6affdcc8c6b5.poster.avif?t=1766084363\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288560/extras/5de6350f5fb0c8e9787e6affdcc8c6b5.webm?t=1766084363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288560/extras/5de6350f5fb0c8e9787e6affdcc8c6b5.mp4?t=1766084363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Game Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relentless Bullet Hell</strong><br>Can you endure attacks that come even from the background? Some cannot be blocked by shields!<br>Keep your shield up and fly constantly to survive!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Saves, Only Skill (Hardcore Experience)</strong><br>There is no save function in this game. Death means returning to the very beginning.<br>Do not despair—through repeated challenges, your control will become sharper than ever.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Guardians of Hell</strong><br>Each floor awaits with massive bosses. Break through their unpredictable patterns and feel the thrill of victory!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288560/extras/abc444fbf9da238eb11f32a81606fd4c.poster.avif?t=1766084363\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288560/extras/abc444fbf9da238eb11f32a81606fd4c.webm?t=1766084363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288560/extras/abc444fbf9da238eb11f32a81606fd4c.mp4?t=1766084363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>2.0 UPDATE: The Evolved Revenge System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Companions Appear</strong>: The lonely fight is over. Meet a reliable partner in hell and conquer the battlefield together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coin Shop &amp; Ring System</strong>: Defeat enemies to collect coins. Buy powerful rings to customize Pudding’s abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Power-Ups</strong>: Your equipment determines the difficulty of escaping hell. Build your own playstyle!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288560/extras/f148d83ffe1d2b1cad117233b53b5d47.avif?t=1766084363\" width=1560 height=578 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>Challenge Toward the True Ending</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escaping hell is not the end. If you reach the ultimate peak and defeat the final boss,<br>the door to the “True Ending” that no one has ever seen will open.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your limits and fulfill Pudding Guy’s lost love.<br>Kick open the gates of hell now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Developer’s Note:</strong> We actively reflected user feedback to balance difficulty and update systems. Painful yet addictive—enjoy the challenge!</p>",
